    "This unit has functions such as on-demand orchestration, simulation and pre-verification, and policy generation.",
    "Tailored to various scenarios, this unit orchestrates multiple models to form a digital twin environment based on the network topology relationship.",
    "Based on this digital twin environment, data can be generated for AI training to enhance AI model generalization.",
    "It can also serve as an interactive environment for AI training, thereby improving the convergence speed of AI models.",
    "It can support the pre-validation of AI models, thereby enhancing the feasibility of network policy and reducing the risk of failures."
